{"ec":"ET00475346","t":"Yajaman","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/yajaman-et00475346-1765368531.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/yajaman-et00475346-1765368531.jpg","d":"Vaanavaraayan is the respected village leader whose word is law. Following his advice, the villagers boycott voting and instead use politicians' bribe money to build basic amenities. His longtime rival, Vallavaraayan, grows even more bitter when Vaanavaraayan marries Vaitheeswari, the woman he desired. As their rivalry intensifies, the village becomes the battleground for ego, love, and power.","rd":"1993-02-18","rt":153,"ct":"U","g":["Action","Drama"],"l":["Tamil"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Rajinikanth","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/rajinikanth-1795-29-12-2016-01-58-24.jpg"],["Meena","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/meena-durairaj-5783-18-09-2017-05-56-52.jpg"],["Napoleon","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/napoleon-6732-28-12-2016-01-33-43.jpg"],["Aishwarya","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/aishwarya-2645-1675400633.jpg"],["M. N. Nambiar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/m.-n.-nambiar-35565-21-06-2017-13-11-19.jpg"],["Goundamani","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/goundamani-5772-24-03-2017-12-47-10.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["R. V. Udayakumar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/r-v-udayakumar-22987-1747050299.jpg"]],"p":[],"m":[],"c":[],"e":[]}}
