{"ec":"ET00001284","t":"Damini","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/et00001284.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/et00001284.jpg","d":"It is the story of Damini (Meenakshi Sheshadri) and her struggle to bring justice to her maid servant who is raped by her brother-in-law. Damini is married to Shekhar Gupta (Rishi Kapoor) and one day she witnesses her brother-in-law, Rakesh (Ashwin Kaushal), raping their maid servant. She rushes to call Shekhar, but its too late.<br/>The family decides to hide the matter from the police to save their reputation, however, Damini goes and complains to the police.<br/>In the court she testifies against Rakesh. But she is portrayed as a mentally unstable person and confined to a mental institution. She escapes the torture and comes across an alcoholic lawyer, Govind (Sunny Deol). He re-opens the case and the rest is how he, Damini and Shekhar bring justice to the maid servant, who dies in the hospital.","rd":"1993-04-30","rt":null,"ct":"30 Apr, 1993","g":["Drama"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Meenakshi Seshadri","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/meenakshi-seshadri-4958-20-11-2017-01-00-28.jpg"],["Sunny Deol","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/sunny-deol-2299-12-09-2017-03-59-10.jpg"],["Rishi Kapoor","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/rishi-kapoor-1883-12-09-2017-06-08-03.jpg"],["Amrish Puri","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/amrish-puri-4574-24-03-2017-17-31-53.jpg"],["Paresh Rawal","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/paresh-rawal-1644-13-09-2017-03-44-45.jpg"],["Rohini Hattangadi","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/rohini-hattangadi-1922-19-04-2017-14-28-24.jpg"],["Kulbhushan Kharbanda","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist